text: Jørgen Tramm (born 27 April 1965) is a Danish rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Danish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Denmark Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Esbjerg
